    <item>
      <title>周末财政简报发布后中国股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/asian-investors-wary-as-china-briefing-underwhelms-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在周末的新闻发布会上，财政部承诺为陷入困境的房地产行业提供更多支持，并暗示将增加政府借款以支撑经济，此后中国股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/asian-investors-wary-as-china-briefing-underwhelms-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 22:21:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国就以色列与伊朗冲突举行新闻发布会 油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-14</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受以色列袭击伊朗的阴影笼罩市场的影响，中国财政部周六召开了备受期待的新闻发布会，会上未提及任何刺激措施以刺激中国这一最大进口国的消费，导致油价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-14</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 22:13:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济学家呼吁中国采取更多行动对抗通货紧缩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-12/china-leaves-economists-wanting-more-action-to-defeat-deflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国进一步加大对经济的支持力度，承诺为低迷的房地产行业和负债累累的地方政府提供更多援助。但官员们仍未让经济学家相信他们已经采取了足够多的措施来战胜通货紧缩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-12/china-leaves-economists-wanting-more-action-to-defeat-deflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 13:00:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
